						<text><![CDATA[<p>Hoborg Labolatories is a home for all my projects. Obviousely it    s all about Hoborg which is the core project (Zend Controllers and library).</p>
<p>You can find out more about Hoborg CMS on <a href="../../../en/cms">its site</a>. All projects in my lab are build and tested on Hudson continues integration server.</p>]]></text>
					</data>
