				<component name="paragraph" id="7" parent-id="4">
					<data>
						<text><![CDATA[
<h3>Build your own <strong>Dashboard</strong></h3>
<p>Hoborg Labolatories released <a href="http://dashboard.hoborglabs.com">Dashboard</a>. It's free, easy to install
and run, distributed dashboard. It comes with handy widgets for pulling data from Jenkins, Trello, Redmine, Github... 
HoborgLabs <a href="/dashboard">got one</a> as well.
</p>
<p>
Do you have multiple servers in your infrastructure? Not a problem - just put a hoborglabs widget on your server
and add it to your dashboard!
</p>
						]]></text>
					</data>
