						<text><![CDATA[
<h3><strong>Bye-bye</strong> Zend.</h3>
<p>Hoborg Labs is moving away form Zend. Next stop: Symfony2, Doctrine2 and Behat2. First module on the list is HoborgCommons - which is now public project and you can 
<a href="https://github.com/hoborglabs">find it on github</a>!</p>
<p>On top of that Hoborg will be getting RESTful APIs. More information and docs comming soon.</p>
]]></text>
					</data>
				</component>
				<component name="paragraph" id="8" parent-id="4">
