						<text><![CDATA[<h3><strong>What's</strong> new?</h3>
<p><strong>Hoborg Dashboard</strong> - It's a status board for Hoborg CMS vital signs. You can check progress, project health, and many more in <a href="../../../en/dashboard">one place</a>.</p>
<p>Something missing? Let us know and we will add new graphs or stats.</p>]]></text>
